Feature:: Create activity
    Description: Create activity for project
    Actor: Employee
    
# Main scenario
Scenario: Create activity as employee with no project manager
    Given there is a project
    And project has no project manager
    And employee with ID "mkr" is logged in
    And employee is part of the project
    And employee is not project manager
    When create activity for project
    Then activity for project created
    
# Alternative scenario
Scenario: Create activity as employee with no project manager
    Given there is a project
    And project has a project manager
    And employee with ID "mkr" is logged in
    And employee is part of the project
    And employee is not project manager
    When create activity for project
    Then activity for project created